@startuml Authentication and Registration Diagram

title Registration, Login, and Logout Flow

actor User
participant "Web App" as App
participant "Auth Service" as Auth

User -> App: Open registration page
User -> App: Submit registration details
App -> Auth: Create user account
Auth --> App: Account created
App --> User: Registration successful

User -> App: Open login page
User -> App: Submit credentials
App -> Auth: Verify credentials
Auth --> App: Return authentication status
App --> User: Login successful

User -> App: Click logout
App -> Auth: Invalidate session
Auth --> App: Session invalidated
App --> User: Logout successful

@enduml